709f.avif?t=1759227782 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個決定都會在你的關係中留下印記，塑造你獨特故事的進程。為你的隊伍尋找新的誘人同伴，並享受與性感女孩的性愛和浪漫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/786864f90d3201e93d65a7504f491e96.avif?t=1759227782\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/4a42c58db4b7633453cba36f9edc041d.avif?t=1759227782\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇情豐富的情節；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高品質的3D地圖供探索和執行任務；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >露骨的性愛場景和CG；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有獨特個性、戰鬥技能和性偏好的隊伍成員；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >數十個可選的NPC進行性事；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多個支線任務；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制戰鬥系統；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各種敵人和怪物；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收藏品和稀有戰利品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.poster.avif?t=1759227782\" width=1170 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.webm?t=1759227782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.mp4?t=1759227782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://s