762840/extras_big/ce9bca9124d90a38b933c7900f62cb3a.avif?t=1759227782 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/786864f90d3201e93d65a7504f491e96.avif?t=1759227782\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/766a433539a1c540962a9dcdcef44bd4.avif?t=1759227782\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在《血色掠奪者》黑暗奇幻世界中等待你的hardcore性冒險和狂野快樂中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/275b78925235309f9d7c58eec5ffa25c.avif?t=1759227782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras_big/275b78925235309f9d7c58eec5ffa25c.avif?t=1759227782 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冥界黑暗的走廊中觀察並參與與赤裸罪人的露骨變態場景，然後在復活後在生者的世界中享受愛與慾望。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/6ace6714d0b3de34320e05bf386bb893.avif?t=1759227782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras_big/6ace6714d0b3de34320e05bf386bb893.avif?t=1759227782 width=1560 height=876 /></span><br><br>與你的隊伍成員建立和探索關係，同時在城鎮、妓院、酒館和各種其他地點與NPC進行自發、熱情的邂逅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/12b199c825fa8b64e77ba8ef5c3c709f.avif?t=1759227782\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras_big/12b199c825fa8b64e77ba8ef5c3c709f.avif?t=1759227782 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個決定都會在你的關係中留下印記，塑造你獨特故事的進程。為你的隊伍尋找新的誘人同伴，並享受與性感女孩的性愛和浪漫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/786864f90d3201e93d65a7504f491e96.avif?t=1759227782\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/4a42c58db4b7633453cba36f9edc041d.avif?t=1759227782\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劇情豐富的情節；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高品質的3D地圖供探索和執行任務；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >露骨的性愛場景和CG；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有獨特個性、戰鬥技能和性偏好的隊伍成員；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >數十個可選的NPC進行性事；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多個支線任務；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制戰鬥系統；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各種敵人和怪物；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收藏品和稀有戰利品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.poster.avif?t=1759227782\" width=1170 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.webm?t=1759227782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/1c5c29d07e743d246e189cb12ad38f72.mp4?t=1759227782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/extras/786864f90d3201e93d65a7504f491e96.avif?t=1759227782\" /></span></p>", "short_description": "遊玩具有回合制戰鬥和探索的等距黑暗奇幻RPG。執行任務，與敵人戰鬥，享受性冒險。為你的血色掠奪者隊伍召集誘人的同伴，拯救王國免受永恆邪惡力量的侵害！😈", "supported_languages": "英文<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/header.jpg?t=1759227782", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1759227782", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762840/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1759227782", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10/11 (64bit)<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3-4340 或更高<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> 支援 OpenGL 4.4 或更高版本的顯示卡。<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10/11 (64bit)<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5-8400 / Ryzen 5 1500X or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 16 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA® GeForce™ GTX1650 AMD Radeon™ RX570<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 15 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}